      "instruction": "<p>Tear the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into small pieces (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Add the <strong>torn mushrooms</strong> and <strong>red onion petals</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and<strong> pomegranate molasses</strong></p><p>Add a generous pinch of<strong> pepper</strong> and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong>, gently mix it all together set aside to marinate – this is your <strong>marinated veg</strong></p>",
